    "department": "Engineering",
    "description": "ABOUT REPRALLY\n\nRepRally is building the future of wholesale commerce. We’re a VC-backed technology startup in NYC, uniting brands, sales reps, and distributors into a single, powerful platform. Our mission: to make wholesale as connected, data-driven, and frictionless as consumer e-commerce.\n\nWe intentionally keep a low profile, but behind the scenes we’re scaling fast — powered by a tight-knit, elite team and backed by leading investors including Infinity Ventures, Indicator Ventures, Mu Ventures, and Clocktower Ventures.\n\n\nWHY THIS ROLE MATTERS\n\nWe’re hiring a Business Recruiter to help us scale the next generation of talent across sales, customer success, and operations. You’ll be the engine behind our growth — identifying, engaging, and closing top performers who thrive in high-velocity, builder environments.\n\nYou’ll own high-volume recruiting across critical GTM and business functions, partner directly with leadership on hiring strategy, and play a key role in shaping the future culture of RepRally as we scale from early traction to industry dominance.\n\n\nWHAT YOU’LL DO\n\n - Lead full-cycle recruiting across sales, success, and operations — from sourcing and outreach to offer and close.\n\n - Partner closely with hiring managers and founders to deeply understand role needs, team structure, and success profiles.\n\n - Build and manage robust candidate pipelines, ensuring smooth and high-touch experiences.\n\n - Develop creative sourcing strategies across LinkedIn, referrals, outbound, and community channels.\n\n - Track funnel performance, hiring velocity, and candidate quality metrics to continuously optimize.\n\n - Represent RepRally’s brand in a competitive market — you’ll be one of the first people candidates meet.\n\n - Contribute to broader hiring process improvements, tooling, and operational excellence.\n\n\nWHAT WE’RE LOOKING FOR\n\n - 4+ years of recruiting experience, ideally starting in an agency environment before moving in-house.\n\n - At least 1+ year of experience at a high-growth startup.\n\n - Demonstrated success managing high-volume business recruiting (sales, customer success, operations).\n\n - Strong communication and relationship-building skills — you can engage everyone from SDRs to senior execs.\n\n - Self-starter who thrives in fast-paced, ambiguous environments.\n\n - Highly organized with a focus on execution, follow-through, and quality.\n\n - Passionate about building — you see recruiting as core to company creation, not just filling seats.\n\n\nWHY YOU’LL LOVE WORKING HERE\n\n - Impact from Day One: You’ll own projects that directly move the needle for the business.\n\n - Elite Team: Work alongside top-tier talent in engineering, product, and sales.\n\n - On-Site Energy: Collaborate in our Manhattan HQ — no Zoom fatigue, just fast decisions and faster builds.\n\n - Competitive Compensation + Equity: Every team member gets meaningful ownership.\n\n - Benefits that have your back:\n   \n   - 99% of medical, dental, and vision premiums covered.\n   \n   - Unlimited PTO (we mean it).",
    "employment_type": "FullTime",
